## Marketing primitives — `src/components/common/`

### `CommonButton.tsx` — pill CTA (Artlist-style)
- Variants: `primary` (gold `bg-brand`, `text-inverse`, `shadow-cta`), `secondary` (white fill, dark text), `outline`, `ghost`
- Sizes: `sm` | `md` | `lg` — wrap with `<Link>` for navigation
- Implementation wraps `@heroui/react/button` with preset classes; use **this** on landing/marketing pages instead of ad-hoc HeroUI styling

### `BrandLogo.tsx`
- Gold square mark + “Nedriva” wordmark; wrap with `<Link href="/">` in header/footer

### `TagPill.tsx`
- Uppercase micro labels (genres, categories): `border-white/12`, `text-subtle`, `rounded-ui-sm`

### `MediaCard.tsx`
- Props: `aspect` (`video` | `square` | `portrait` | `landscape`), optional `label`, `overlay`, `hoverLift`
- Children should fill the frame (e.g. `next/image` with `fill`); content is absolutely positioned inside the aspect box

### `SectionHeader.tsx`
- Props: `badge`, `title`, `titleGradient`, `subtitle`, `align`, `action` (e.g. “View all” link), `titleGlow` (uses `text-glow-heading`)
- Section titles use `font-display` for serif marketing look

